author: tensorflower-gardener
message:
Disable MSAN for GPU profiler tests.

The `nomsan` tag is added to `//third_party/tensorflow/compiler/xla/backends/profiler/gpu:cuda_version_variants_test` to disable MemorySanitizer for CUDA-related tests.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 840326645

files.patch:
@@ -132,6 +132,7 @@ xla_cc_test(
         "cuda-only",
         "gpu",
         "no_mac",
+        "nomsan",  # Disable  msan for cuda related tests.
         "requires-gpu-nvidia",
     ],
     deps = [
